1 SECTION 3. It is the intent of this Act not to;
2 (1) Jeopardize the receipt of any federal aid nor to
3 impair the obligation of the State or any of its
4 agencies to the holders of any bond issued by the
5 State or by any of its agencies;
6 (2) Cause the State or any of its agencies to transfer
7 moneys that are encumbered prior to or on the
8 effective date of this Act;
9 (3) Cause the State or any of its agencies to be unable to
10 meet a contractual obligation; and
